<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT35">
<l>tāḷā lulaka maḷanta vacaivēkol</l>
<l>vāḷā kiṭantaruḷum vāytiṟavā ṉīḷōtam</l>
<l>vantalaikku māmayilai māvallik kēṇiyā</l>
<l>ṉaintalaivāy nākat taṇai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[The Lord] from the great Allikkēṇi—by the great Mayilai</l>
<l rend="indent">where high waves come and dash [against the shores],</l>
<l>graciously lies silently on the bed of serpent with five heads [and] mouths—</l>
<l>will not open [His] mouth.</l>
<l>Is [this due to] the weariness of measuring the world with [His] feet?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
